title: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Austria Buildings, Austria, 2008
name: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Austria Buildings, Austria, 2008
description: This data set shows the locations and outlines of over 2,000 buildings in Austria, many of which are public museums, and government buildings. Data was uploaded as a polygon shapefile, not all buildings are labeled, but many are labeled by name.
